<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Stack Overflow</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/styles.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/toastr.js/latest/toastr.min.css">
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.5.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.16.0/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/toastr.js/latest/toastr.min.js"></script>
    <script>
        toastr.options = {
            "closeButton": true,
            "debug": false,
            "newestOnTop": true,
            "progressBar": true,
            "positionClass": "toast-top-right",
            "preventDuplicates": false,
            "onclick": null,
            "showDuration": "300",
            "hideDuration": "1000",
            "timeOut": "2000",
            "extendedTimeOut": "1000",
            "showEasing": "swing",
            "hideEasing": "linear",
            "showMethod": "fadeIn",
            "hideMethod": "fadeOut"
        };
    </script>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="content">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo-container">
                <a href="/" class="logo">
                    <img src="media/logo.png" alt="My Restaurant" class="logoImage">
                </a>
            </div>
            <p class="stack-name">Stack Overflow</p>
            <div class="header-right">
                <a class="active" href="/login">Login</a>
                <a href="/register">Sign Up</a>
            </div>
        </div> 
        <section class="stack-info">
            <div class="info-content">
                <h1>Welcome to Stack Overflow</h1>
                <p>Welcome to Stack Overflow, the ultimate destination for developers around the world. At Stack Overflow, we are dedicated to fostering a vibrant community where developers can seek solutions, share knowledge, and grow together. Our platform is built on the principles of collaboration and continuous learning, providing a space where every question finds its answer and every solution is shared for the benefit of all. Whether you're a seasoned programmer or just starting out, Stack Overflow offers a rich resource of insights, tutorials, and expert advice. Join us in creating a knowledge hub where innovation thrives and coding challenges are conquered. Experience the power of community-driven development at Stack Overflow, where every question sparks a journey of discovery and every answer contributes to the collective wisdom of developers worldwide.</p>
                
                <div class="specialties">
                    <h2>Our Highlights</h2>
                    <ul>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-code"></i> Access a vast library of Q&A on programming and software development</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-code"></i> Engage with a global community of developers and experts</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-code"></i> Find solutions to your coding challenges in real-time</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-code"></i> Discover new technologies and best practices</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                
                <div class="ambiance">
                    <h2>Community</h2>
                    <p>Join millions of developers worldwide in sharing knowledge and building your coding skills.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="services">
                    <h2>Features</h2>
                    <ul>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-comments"></i> Active discussion forums and chat rooms</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-users"></i> Profile customization and reputation system</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i> Personalized feed based on your interests</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-search"></i> Advanced search capabilities to find answers quickly</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                
                <div class="testimonials">
                    <h2>What Our Customers Say</h2>
                    <div class="testimonial">
                        <blockquote>
                            "Stack Overflow has been my go-to place for learning and troubleshooting. It's an invaluable resource."
                        </blockquote>
                        <cite>- John Smith</cite>
                    </div>
                    <div class="testimonial">
                        <blockquote>
                            "The community here is amazing! I've received help from experts around the world."
                        </blockquote>
                        <cite>- Jane Doe</cite>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
    <div class = "footer">
        <p>&copy; 2024 Stack Overflow Clone. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
